    "style": "Heading 1",
    "text": "6. Charter Management Framework *(NEW --- Gap Closure)*"
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 2",
    "text": "6.1 Charter Purpose & Authority"
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 2",
    "text": "6.2 8 Mandatory Charter Elements"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "1 Purpose Statement of why the data governance program exists, its strategic alignment, and expected outcomes Charter document section 1"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "2 Scope Definition of what data, systems, departments, and activities are in scope vs. out of scope Charter document section 2 + scope boundary registry"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "3 Roles Enumeration of governance roles (owner, 5 steward types, DMO, DPO, ODIAO) with high-level responsibilities Charter document section 3 + RACI reference"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "4 Governance Structure Definition of governance bodies (DGSC, Data Council, Domain Councils, Working Groups), composition, and authority levels Charter document section 4 + org chart"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "5 Decision-Making Process Description of how governance decisions are made, including decision types, approval authorities, and escalation paths Charter document section 5 + Decision Rights Matrix"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "6 Resource Requirements Budget, staffing (DGPO sizing), technology, and training resources allocated to the program Charter document section 6 + budget registry"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "7 Success Criteria Measurable objectives for the governance program including KPIs, maturity targets, and compliance goals Charter document section 7 + KPI dashboard"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "8 Review Cycle Mandatory review frequency (minimum: annually) and trigger conditions for extraordinary review Charter document section 8 + review schedule"
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 2",
    "text": "6.3 Charter Lifecycle Workflow"
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 3",
    "text": "State Model"
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 3",
    "text": "Workflow Stages"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "1. Draft Creation DMO Governance Ops Create charter document using DGOP template with all 8 mandatory elements; populate from entity profile 5 business days"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "2. Working Group Review DG Working Group Review charter draft for completeness, accuracy, and alignment with entity structure 5 business days"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "3. Data Council Review Data Council Review and approve charter content; recommend amendments 5 business days"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "4. DGSC Approval DGSC Chair Final approval and ratification; CEO endorsement 5 business days"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "5. Publication DMO Publish active charter to DGOP; notify all governance role holders; store as governance evidence 1 business day"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "6. Annual Review Trigger DGOP System Auto-generate review case 60 days before annual review due date Automatic"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "7. Amendment Workflow Any governance body Amendment requests follow stages 2-4; version control maintains history Per standard SLA"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "8. Archival DMO Superseded versions archived with full audit trail; evidence chain maintained Automatic on new version approval"
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 3",
    "text": "Charter Version Control"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
