    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Volume 1 -- Executive & Business Design (Enhanced) concludes here. This volume established:"
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Volume 2 -- Functional Design will detail the core modules, universal case management layer, workflow engine BPMN diagrams, and functional specifications for each DGOP capability."
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Volume 3 -- NDI Domain Operational Models will provide detailed operational lifecycles for all 12 NDI domains."
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Volume 4 -- Technical Design will cover architecture, technology stack, integration patterns, API specifications, event architecture, and database design."
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Volume 5 -- Security & Compliance will map NCA ECC controls and PDPL requirements to DGOP capabilities."
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Volume 6 -- Procurement & Delivery will define non-functional requirements, environment strategy, acceptance criteria, UAT scenarios, support model, and implementation roadmap."
  }
